{"tid":815251,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"知道就快會分手 但唔想攤牌","createTime":"2018-09-12T02:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T13:36:18.000Z","uid":115104,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4bdb576c995c042bf0b2d162d50fcd06578e6f93","tid":815251,"uid":115104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"文長 辛苦大家<br />\n但真係好辛苦 一直要扮無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同女朋友拍左就快4年拖<br />\n中間冷靜左2-3次 但最後都一齊返<br />\n最近女朋友係我面前覆Whatsapp 見到揀表情符號果版<br />\n好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心心 kiss 既 emoji<br />\n覺得好奇怪 因為我同佢既whatsapp 好小出現呢D emoji<br />\n果刻心都涼一涼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呃自己冇事既<br />\n<br />\n不過呃到自己未必呃到人<br />\n朋友同我講 問我做咩fb 小左咁多女朋友既相<br />\n我開出黎話冇小到<br />\n但朋友用佢 fb show 出黎 係冇哂我同女朋友既合照<br />\n原來女朋友將所有合照都set左 被標示的人<br />\n最後發現 我地兩個今年影既雙方生日相 同 食物相 女朋友都Del哂<br />\n就連佢upload 單人照 我比左心心既相 都del埋<br />\n呢刻我好明白 我只係等被人宣佈死刑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解明明就想分開 但又要拖我手 錫我<br />\n送禮物比我<br />\n仲要送月餅比我屋企<br />\n以前好鐘意佢笑 而家佢對住我笑<br />\n我好心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc978e0766bc5620d1cdb7c257dd7b71231d3df","tid":815251,"uid":107649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"無套中出一波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda17f3b9e2b5a815009427d197f2a6f726fcb90","tid":815251,"uid":115104,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0fc978e0766bc5620d1cdb7c257dd7b71231d3df","tid":815251,"uid":107649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"無套中出一波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"同女朋友 有2 3個月冇做愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46226bf01cd9b43fd6e545e2b0054b2105c7a656","tid":815251,"uid":41992,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無套中出一波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>同女朋友 有2 3個月冇做愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中出埋最後一次 飛左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個好好咁傾下啦 4年話長唔長話短唔短<br />\n佢如果唔係有第二個 有得傾架 最緊要都係溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188f722cdb1cd381c2280c4addb113604421c223","tid":815251,"uid":29487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:16:29.000Z","msg":"慘, 唔鐘意又拖住人正仆街"},{"pid":"4ddfbddba41abcdd529a225586c0b1639fea7543","tid":815251,"uid":208364,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T02:17:14.000Z","msg":"問清楚，你女朋友真係唔想再同你行嘅，就放手啦，唔好困死自己，未來大把嘢等梗你，人地都做到咁，留返最後嘅尊嚴比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.